snippet.title: INDIA'S GOT LATENT Bouncer Breaks Character | Dostcast w/ Amin Khan
snippet.description:
Amin Khan is a professional bodyguard and has been a bouncer for 18 years in Mumbai. He was a Maharashtra-level bodybuilder and has provided security to celebrities like Poonam Pandey and Nora Fatehi. He has also acted in movies like Ready with Salman Khan. Currently, he is a bouncer on Samay RainaтАЩs show IndiaтАЩs Got Latent.

In this episode, Vinamre and Amin talk about:

тАвHis early days during his bodybuilding career and the consumption of steroids
тАвThe craziest experiences of being a bouncer, Handling crowds in high-pressure situations
тАвThe process of securing VIPs in different scenarios, How celebrities are in real life
тАвHis experience working with Salman Khan in a movie and Amitabh Bachchan in KBC
тАвThe struggles and challenges faced by bouncers, His experiences in dance bars and clubs

Watch this episode to uncover the real-life story of Andrew Tate of IndiaтАЩs Got Latent.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.
